<subsection><title>Wrap-Up</title>
<p>In this Lesson, we worked on the following skills and goals related to logarithms:</p>
<p><ul>
<li><p>Find the doubling time or half-life of an exponential function</p></li>    
<li><p>Write exponential functions using doubling time and half-life</p></li>
</ul></p>

